<!-- About -->
  <section>
   <h2> About </h2>
    <p> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Martin_Scorsese" target="_blank"> Martin Scorsese </a> is an American director, producer, screenwriter, and film historian. He was born in 1942 and has had a career that spans more than 50 years. <br> He is the founder of <i> The Film Foundation </i> and the <i> World Cinema Foundation </i>. He has directed a variety of films, starring incredible actors. </p>

    <figure>
      <img src="../Class Code/Influential-Imgs/Scorsese-and-Leo.jpg" height="300px" width="auto" alt="Leo and Scorsese">
      <figcaption> Leonardo DiCaprio has often starred in his movies! <br>
      Photo is from <a href="http://osagenews.org/en/" target="_blank"> Osage News </a> </figcaption>
    </figure>

